languages.text: "Идут, грядут, след в след друг за другом — Заря утренняя, затем — вечерняя".
"They are coming, one following in the other's footsteps: the Aurora of the morning and the Aurora of the evening."
languages.original_text: "Идут, грядут, след в след друг за другом — Заря утренняя, затем — вечерняя".

traits.locale_text: "They are coming, one walking in the other's footsteps, the twin Auroras: she of the morning and she of the evening."

languages.text: "Sie kommen, eine tritt in die Fußstapfen der anderen, die Aurora des Morgens und die Aurora des Abends."
languages.original_text: "They are coming, one following in the other's footsteps: the Aurora of the morning and the Aurora of the evening."

traits.locale_text: "Sie kommen, eine tritt in die Fußstapfen der anderen, die Zwillingsauroras: die des Morgens und die des Abends."

languages.text: « Elles arrivent, marchant dans les pas l'une de l'autre, l'Aurore du matin et l'Aurore du soir. »
languages.original_text: "They are coming, one following in the other's footsteps: the Aurora of the morning and the Aurora of the evening."

traits.locale_text: « Elles arrivent, marchant dans les pas l'une de l'autre, les Aurores jumelles : celle du matin et celle du soir. »

languages.text: “极光双子，她们来了，紧挨着彼此的脚步。她代表清晨，她代表夜晚。”
languages.original_text: "They are coming, one following in the other's footsteps: the Aurora of the morning and the Aurora of the evening."

traits.locale_text: “极光双子，她们来了，紧挨着彼此的脚步。她代表清晨，她代表夜晚。”

languages.text: 「彼女達が来る。片方がもう片方の足跡を辿って来る。そう、朝のオーロラと夕方のオーロラだ」
languages.original_text: "They are coming, one following in the other's footsteps: the Aurora of the morning and the Aurora of the evening."

traits.locale_text: 「彼女達が来る。片方がもう片方の足跡を辿って来る。双子のオーロラ。朝の彼女と夕方の彼女だ」

languages.text: «Vienen, una siguiendo los pasos de la otra, la Aurora de la mañana y la Aurora de la tarde».
languages.original_text: "They are coming, one following in the other's footsteps: the Aurora of the morning and the Aurora of the evening."

traits.locale_text: «Vienen, una siguiendo los pasos de la otra, las Auroras gemelas: la de la mañana y la de la tarde».

languages.text: "Geliyorlar, birinin izi diğerine karışıyor. Gündüzün ve gecenin Aurora'sı nihayet geliyor."
languages.original_text: "They are coming, one following in the other's footsteps: the Aurora of the morning and the Aurora of the evening."

traits.locale_text: "Geliyorlar, bir kafile misali yaklaşıyorlar. Gündüzün ve gecenin Aurora'sı nihayet geliyor."
